@node ARENA "Arena"

@{b}Arena@{ub}

Rarity  = Uncommon
Type    = Land
Artist  = Rob Alexander

Text(PR): <3T>: Choose one of your creatures and have your opponent choose
          one of his or her creatures. Both target creatures become tapped.
          Your creature does its power in damage to your opponent's creature,
          and your opponent's creature does its power in damage to yours.

