@node MANAC "Mana Crypt"

@{b}Mana Crypt@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = Uncommon
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 0
Artist  = Mark Tedin

Text(PR): During your upkeep, flip a coin. Opponent calls heads or tails
          while coin is in the air. If flip ends up in opponent's favor,
          Mana Crypt deals 3 damage to you.
          <T>: Add two colorless mana to  your mana pool.
          Play this ability as an interrupt.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_M.guide/MANCR}

